Participants’ ability and skills and their vehicles’ capabilities were tested to the highest standards. Gasoline Alley and Liqui Moly sponsored the event, while Predator Paintball also contributed towards the day’s fun with some paintball matches. Participants in the 4×4 event competed in a modified and standard class. The next event will take place on 31 July. This will be a Top Truck challenge together with Predator Paintball and Propshaft Specialists. Results: Modified 1. Bernard Radmore. 2. Werner Janse van Vuuren. 3. Renier Janse van Vuuren Standard 1. Dewald Brill Venter. 2. Heimrich Swart.